      ******************************************************************
      *                    ESCRITA NO LOG DE ALTERACOES                *
      ******************************************************************
       VIAP0010-GERA-LOG.

           CALL VIAL0010-PGMID USING VIAL0001-COMMAREA
                                     VIAL0002-COMMAREA
                                     VIAL0010-COMMAREA





           ON EXCEPTION
             SET ETCL0002-ERROS-ARQ    TO TRUE
             MOVE VIAK0001-PROG-NOTFND  TO ETCL0002-NR-ERRO
             MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS    TO ETCL0002-CAPLIC-ERRO
             MOVE VIAL0010-PGMID        TO ETCL0002-CPROGRAM.

       VIAP0010-GERA-LOG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

